{"tid":1372292,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[支線任務］元朗鄉黑勢力必須瓦解","createTime":"2019-07-27T11:44:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T17:41:13.000Z","uid":21552,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e2af72f28943ef2a3808200d325aa133ae5f2b27","tid":1372292,"uid":21552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T11:44:35.000Z","msg":"想同大家講下點解削去鄉黑勢力咁重要！<br />\n<br />\n佢哋同支那有微妙關係，可以話係副線。<br />\n<br />\n1. 回歸後儲落嘅勢力，很多鄉黑已滲透到不同政府部門：你睇下八鄉光頭指揮官，再睇下二哥鄧副處長。所以好多政府部門都放過鄉黑做違法嘅事，小事如僭建，大事如打人放火做假數。<br />\n<br />\n2. 幫手做d唔可以光明正大做嘅事：恐嚇迫使正氣議員放棄參選、元朗黑夜不多講。<br />\n<br />\n3. 新界土地：鄉黑做地產、發展商。暴力收地，高價賣比政府撈油水。<br />\n<br />\n4. 依個年代仲玩丁權？我哋香港人咁辛苦儲錢買樓做咩。<br />\n<br />\n5. 非法佔用官地，用來做民生嘅地發展無期。<br />\n<br />\n6. 現在士氣高昂，打住反黑旗號有利而無一害。<br />\n<br />\n仲有好多好多，對抗一個強大嘅政權，先除去其鷹犬是必須。黑警係狗，鄉黑就係鷹！<br />\n<br />\n對抗方法就要集思廣益<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人加油！"},{"pid":"c1c70e5abeeac3f4cdc29aab9baccb46679b2c0e","tid":1372292,"uid":181778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T11:45:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e9bf70b6ae73cf1fa03f3ac945d93b26505c4217","tid":1372292,"uid":181778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T11:45:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"31ae0385f2a223ad44607670decf28dd15005afa","tid":1372292,"uid":21552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e9bf70b6ae73cf1fa03f3ac945d93b26505c4217","tid":1372292,"uid":181778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T11:45:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T11:57:04.000Z","msg":"你對準政府，次次大嗰粒下台，慢慢就到嗰時安排好嘅鄉黑上到高位。<br />\n<br />\n鄉黑清算易好多，所以話係支線，而且有即時嘅效果！"},{"pid":"a5129d2d140e7944fe2b6f6b9e424755715f65a6","tid":1372292,"uid":114798,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e9bf70b6ae73cf1fa03f3ac945d93b26505c4217","tid":1372292,"uid":181778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T11:45:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T12:03:52.000Z","msg":"對咩準政府<br />\n林鄭跟本都無實權<br />\n呢家根本中共直接控制黑警<br />\n軍政府狀態"},{"pid":"e1040cce4d7a8e929ea6dee87ed0465bed7ef79e","tid":1372292,"uid":181778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T12:04:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0b8242ceb0242f04d7987be8908355d956ed6726","tid":1372292,"uid":21552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:47:08.000Z","msg":"過咗今晚更加要推<br />\n鄉黑係依家黑狗死穴 所以先咁緊張"},{"pid":"598ee623049f230a49ed4075f5751ffec0a09303","tid":1372292,"uid":21552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:01:58.000Z","msg":"今晚已有葉虎證據 更加證明我講嘅係正確"},{"pid":"0fc0677727a1f572caba2826b6a76f8eea026a68","tid":1372292,"uid":123738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:06:50.000Z","msg":"丁屋最多咪起多兩層你吹鳩脹咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f428039447c7966efc2f65f64c602c27645c7f8c","tid":1372292,"uid":21552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0fc0677727a1f572caba2826b6a76f8eea026a68","tid":1372292,"uid":123738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:06:50.000Z","msg":"丁屋最多咪起多兩層你吹鳩脹咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:12:57.000Z","msg":"咁大塊地益鄉黑 仲要係因為過時嘅傳統規矩"},{"pid":"05f3fdaaa076363f2d530a8c56ad5764c3b14dc4","tid":1372292,"uid":21552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:19:03.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"b3525384b4c9da0733b902b0d44613a4a7f704e0","tid":1372292,"uid":21552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:00:33.000Z","msg":"今次運動揭開好多政府黑暗面<br />\n我哋依家仲係咪剩係得五大訴求呢？"},{"pid":"6078d87fe95c9a49bfb4a5b74e929187d6255ce5","tid":1372292,"uid":115977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:03:27.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"30a473aec190919d8bc40a874399d62269495440","tid":1372292,"uid":221743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score